Interface SharedMessages.VehicleService

  • Enclosing interface:
    SharedMessages

    public static interface SharedMessages.VehicleService
    Verticle exchange messages addresses for the VehicleService. They are being used at the VehicleService startup in order to bind the proper exchange before deploying the application Verticles.
